July 31 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Thursday. To inform us of other job changes, email moves@thomsonreuters.com.

BARCLAYS PLC <BARC.L> Barclays has hired Marc Chowrimootoo from Bank of American Merrill Lynch <BAC.N> to join its leveraged finance team in Europe, a person familiar with the matter said. [ID:nL6N0Q55T8]  SEI INVESTMENTS CO <SEIC.O>